年，毛泽东在《新民主主义论》中阐述了新民主主义的政治、经济和文化，故A选项错误。1949年6月30日，毛泽东发表《论人民民主专政》一文，故B选项错误。《为建设一个伟大的社会主义国家而奋斗》毛泽东1954年9月15日在中华人民共和国第一届全国人民代表大会第一次会议上的开幕词。故D选项错误。故本题正确答案为C选项。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":13888,"correctTimesAmount":8465,"accuracyAmount":61.0,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000+00:00","sourceExerId":null,"scoreRules":null,"scoreLess":null,"newKeyType":1,"isUnorderedMate":0,"isMaterial":0,"wrongSource":null,"score":null,"typeName":null,"isFinishs":0,"accuracy":null,"progressPercentage":null,"questionNumber":null,"questionAllNumber":null,"starCount":0,"sourceType":null,"collectionType":null,"cstId":null,"userKey":null,"wrongSum":null,"myCollectionld":null,"linkName":null,"simNum":null,"simScore":null,"answerTypeId":null,"index":2,"myCollectionId":0,"exerEcontent":null,"exerJcontent":null,"userKeyImg1":null,"userKeyImg2":null,"userKeyImg3":null,"isCorrect":null,"rightKeyList":["C"],"simExamScore":null,"sonExer":[],"answerType":"单选","exerNum":null,"prname":"第二部分 毛泽东思想和中国特色社会主义理论体系概论>第五章 社会主义建设道路初步探索的理论成果"},{"exerID":4326255,"title":"中国共产党探索中国自己建设社会主义道路开始的标志是（ ）。","courseID":"H011901","catID":943806,"optNum":4,"a":"中共八大的召开。","b":"《论十大关系》的发表","c":"社会主义三大改造的开始","d":"国民经济恢复的完成","e":null,"f":null,"g":null,"h":null,"rightKey":"B","keyType":"单选","analyze":"中国共产党探索中国自己建设社会主义道路开始的标志是1956年4月《论十大关系》的发表。故B选项符合题意。","matRef":null,"diffCoeff":1,"freqCoeff":1,"exerType":"章节题","source":"章节题","isValid":1,"isMultiExer":1,"multiExerID":null,"isHtmlTag":0,"pracTimesAmount":13874,"correctTimesAmount":9642,"accuracyAmount":69.5,"reviewExerGroupID":0,"exerGroupId":0,"subTitle":null,"econtent":null,"jcontent":null,"agencyId":0,"isAudit":1,"adminId":0,"auditId":31106,"auditTime":null,"createTime":"2024-06-25T06:23:15.000